<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>خ و ص<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٧٠٤ - خ و ص]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>خوَّصَ يُخوِّص، تخويصًا، فهو مخوِّص<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• خوَّصَت النَّخلةُ:</span> أورقت، تشقَّقت عن الخوص فبدا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• خوَّصت الأرضُ:</span> كان بها خُوصٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>